===Adjective===
'''minus'''
#{{mathematics}} [[Negative]].
#:''a minus number''
#On the negative part of a [[scale]].
#:'''''minus''' seven degrees''
#[[Rank]]ing just below a designated rating.
#:''He got a grade of B '''minus''' for his essay.''

